Sping multiple vagrant machines of CentOS7 with one command for clustering.

Requirements:
    * Virtualbox-5.0
    * Vagrant-1.8.5 or greater

How to do it:

$ cd multiple-vagrant-machines

$ ./build-machines.sh

Above script will automatically pull the official CentOS7 box from vagrant cloud and spin 4-machines (1-master, 2-slaves, 1-nginx)

Script will automatically update the instances and install basic softwares during the provision.

Script will automatically takes the public IP from your Host NIC. No matter if you are using multipl NIC's.

At the end script will display the IP's of all the instances and SSH into the master instance.
